2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with content delivery in a network setting, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a delivery scheme that exploits receiver side information, which involves the use of algorithms and data structures. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with a system that has state feedback, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with content delivery, which is a key problem in multimedia systems.
